      "span_text": "These findings suggest that dendritically localized synaptic plasticity-related mRNAs like Arc are markers of where synaptic plasticity is occurring and that BLA activation is a regulator of when it occurs. [CITATION_2] recently found that glutamate induced rapid translation of ARC in hippocampal dendrites and that reactivation of stalled polyribosomes mediated this effect."
